---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Intelligence | Levenhall" description="Levenhall Intelligence is a live geopolitical operating picture for the corporate risk function. Live at intel.levenhall.com.">

    <!-- ── HERO ── -->
    <section class="i-hero">
        <div class="i-hero-glow"></div>
        <div class="i-hero-grid"></div>
        <div class="i-hero-scan"></div>

        <span class="i-hud i-hud-tl"></span>
        <span class="i-hud i-hud-tr"></span>
        <span class="i-hud i-hud-bl"></span>
        <span class="i-hud i-hud-br"></span>

        <div class="i-hero-stage">
            <p class="i-hero-tag">A Levenhall Product</p>
            <p class="i-hero-pre">Levenhall</p>
            <h1 class="i-wordmark">INTELLIGENCE</h1>
            <p class="i-hero-tagline">Geopolitical intelligence for the corporate risk function.</p>

            <div class="i-hero-meta">
                <span class="i-meta-dot"></span>
                <span class="i-meta-text">Live at <a href="https://intel.levenhall.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">intel.levenhall.com</a></span>
            </div>

            <div class="i-hero-cta">
                <a href="https://intel.levenhall.com" class="btn btn-gold" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Open the Dashboard</a>
                <a href="#how" class="btn btn-outline-white">How It Works</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── OPENING ── -->
    <section class="i-opening">
        <div class="i-prose reveal">
            <p class="i-lede">The risk events that move share prices, disrupt supply chains, and reshape market access do not announce themselves in the news cycle. They surface in signal &mdash; weeks or months before the headlines.</p>
            <p>Levenhall Intelligence is the operating picture we built for the corporate risk function. Enterprise risk officers, geopolitical risk leads, supply chain teams, security functions, and investment committees with international exposure all work the same way: one screen, every layer, on a globe that updates in real time.</p>
            <p>Heavy machine learning runs in a Web Worker on your own device. Nothing leaves the browser. No round-trip to our servers.</p>
            <p class="i-lede-close">Open it. The rest of this page explains what you'll see.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── THE CII (CENTERPIECE) ── -->
    <section class="i-cii" id="how">
        <div class="i-cii-stage">
            <header class="i-cii-head reveal">
                <span class="i-eyebrow i-eyebrow-gold">§ The proprietary layer</span>
                <h2>The Country Instability Index.</h2>
                <p>A composite 0&ndash;100 score across thirty-one countries that drive corporate risk exposure &mdash; markets where your supply chain runs, your assets sit, or your operating environment can change overnight.</p>
            </header>

            <figure class="i-formula reveal">
                <figcaption class="i-formula-label">Blended Score</figcaption>
                <pre class="i-formula-code"><span class="i-fc-b">(</span><span class="i-fc-v">Baseline Risk</span> <span class="i-fc-op">×</span> <span class="i-fc-n">0.4</span><span class="i-fc-b">)</span> <span class="i-fc-op">+</span> <span class="i-fc-b">(</span><span class="i-fc-v">Event Score</span> <span class="i-fc-op">×</span> <span class="i-fc-n">0.6</span><span class="i-fc-b">)</span>
<span class="i-fc-op">+</span> <span class="i-fc-v">Hotspot Boost</span>
<span class="i-fc-op">+</span> <span class="i-fc-v">News Urgency Boost</span>
<span class="i-fc-op">+</span> <span class="i-fc-v">Focal Point Boost</span>
<span class="i-fc-op">+</span> <span class="i-fc-v">Displacement Boost</span>
<span class="i-fc-op">+</span> <span class="i-fc-v">Climate Stress</span></pre>
            </figure>

            <div class="i-cii-foot reveal">
                <p>The Event Score itself is weighted: <span class="i-tag i-tag-conf">Conflict 30%</span> <span class="i-tag i-tag-unr">Unrest 25%</span> <span class="i-tag i-tag-inf">Information 25%</span> <span class="i-tag i-tag-sec">Security 20%</span>. Active wars score 70 or higher automatically. A million displaced adds 8. Each country carries a multiplier from 0.3× to 3× to compensate for media suppression and expected event frequency.</p>
                <div class="i-tier-row">
                    <span class="i-tier-lbl">Output</span>
                    <span class="i-tier i-tier-low">Low</span>
                    <span class="i-tier i-tier-norm">Normal</span>
                    <span class="i-tier i-tier-elev">Elevated</span>
                    <span class="i-tier i-tier-high">High</span>
                    <span class="i-tier i-tier-crit">Critical</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── HOW IT WORKS ── -->
    <section class="i-how">
        <div class="i-how-frame">
            <header class="i-how-head reveal">
                <span class="i-eyebrow">§ Around the index</span>
                <h2>Five more layers, briefly.</h2>
            </header>

            <article class="i-mod reveal">
                <span class="i-mod-num">02</span>
                <div>
                    <h3>Geo-Convergence</h3>
                    <p>The globe split into 1&deg; grid cells. When conflict, protest, military, and news signals cluster in the same cell within twenty-four hours, the system flags an emerging hotspot &mdash; before mainstream reporting catches up.</p>
                </div>
            </article>
            <article class="i-mod reveal">
                <span class="i-mod-num">03</span>
                <div>
                    <h3>Strategic Risk Composite</h3>
                    <p>One score per region. Geo-convergence at thirty percent, the CII at fifty, infrastructure cascade risk at twenty. The single number a board paper can carry.</p>
                </div>
            </article>
            <article class="i-mod reveal">
                <span class="i-mod-num">04</span>
                <div>
                    <h3>Signal Aggregation</h3>
                    <p>A unified bus that ingests conflict, unrest, economy, cyber, military, and climate streams, prioritizes by urgency, and feeds the rest of the dashboard.</p>
                </div>
            </article>
            <article class="i-mod reveal">
                <span class="i-mod-num">05</span>
                <div>
                    <h3>On-Device ML</h3>
                    <p>Four ONNX models in a Web Worker: MiniLM for embeddings, DistilBERT for sentiment, FLAN-T5 for summarization, BERT for named-entity recognition. Two-hundred-megabyte budget. Zero server roundtrips.</p>
                </div>
            </article>
            <article class="i-mod reveal">
                <span class="i-mod-num">06</span>
                <div>
                    <h3>Infrastructure Cascade</h3>
                    <p>Models dependencies between undersea cables, power grids, pipelines, and data centers. One disruption tells you what falls next &mdash; useful when your operations run through any of them.</p>
                </div>
            </article>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── MAP & COVERAGE ── -->
    <section class="i-map">
        <div class="i-prose reveal">
            <span class="i-eyebrow">§ The globe</span>
            <h2>34 layers on a WebGL globe. 31 markets you can drill into.</h2>
            <p>Eleven layers default on &mdash; conflicts, military assets, sanctions, hotspots, nuclear facilities, infrastructure outages. Twenty-three more a click away &mdash; undersea cables, pipelines, AIS tracking, cyber threats, displacement camps, financial centers, commodity hubs.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="i-cov reveal">
            <div class="i-cov-row">
                <span class="i-cov-cat i-cov-allied">Core &amp; Allied</span>
                <span class="i-cov-flags">🇺🇸 🇬🇧 🇫🇷 🇩🇪 🇵🇱 🇦🇺</span>
            </div>
            <div class="i-cov-row">
                <span class="i-cov-cat i-cov-adv">Sanctioned &amp; Adversarial</span>
                <span class="i-cov-flags">🇷🇺 🇨🇳 🇮🇷 🇰🇵</span>
            </div>
            <div class="i-cov-row">
                <span class="i-cov-cat i-cov-conf">Active Conflict</span>
                <span class="i-cov-flags">🇺🇦 🇸🇾 🇾🇪 🇲🇲 🇸🇩 🇪🇹 🇨🇩 🇸🇴 🇦🇫 🇮🇶 🇱🇾 🇳🇬 🇱🇧</span>
            </div>
            <div class="i-cov-row">
                <span class="i-cov-cat i-cov-reg">Strategic Emerging</span>
                <span class="i-cov-flags">🇮🇳 🇵🇰 🇸🇦 🇹🇷 🇦🇪 🇧🇷 🇻🇪 🇹🇼</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── CTA ── -->
    <section class="i-cta">
        <div class="i-cta-glow"></div>
        <div class="i-cta-inner">
            <span class="i-cta-dot"></span>
            <p class="i-cta-eyebrow">Live Now</p>
            <h2>Open the dashboard.</h2>
            <p>Email-gated. Free to enter. Enterprise deployments and bespoke briefings available through Levenhall's intelligence practice.</p>
            <div class="btn-group" style="justify-content: center;">
                <a href="https://intel.levenhall.com" class="btn btn-gold" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">intel.levenhall.com</a>
                <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline-white">Contact Levenhall</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
    /* ───────────── HERO ───────────── */
    .i-hero {
        background:
            radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 50%, rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.06), transparent 70%),
            radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 50% at 50% 30%, rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.1), transparent 60%),
            #04060c;
        padding: var(--s-20) var(--s-3) var(--s-12);
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        min-height: 88vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
    }

    .i-hero-glow {
        position: absolute;
        top: 50%;
        left: 50%;
        width: 760px;
        height: 760px;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.14) 0%, transparent 60%);
        filter: blur(48px);
        pointer-events: none;
    }

    .i-hero-grid {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background-image:
            linear-gradient(rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
            linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
        background-size: 80px 80px;
        pointer-events: none;
        mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, black 25%, transparent 75%);
        -webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, black 25%, transparent 75%);
    }

    .i-hero-scan {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02) 50%, transparent 50%);
        background-size: 100% 3px;
        pointer-events: none;
        mix-blend-mode: overlay;
        opacity: 0.35;
    }

    .i-hud {
        position: absolute;
        width: 40px;
        height: 40px;
        border: 2px solid var(--gold);
        opacity: 0.55;
    }
    .i-hud-tl { top: 28px; left: 28px; border-right: none; border-bottom: none; }
    .i-hud-tr { top: 28px; right: 28px; border-left: none; border-bottom: none; }
    .i-hud-bl { bottom: 28px; left: 28px; border-right: none; border-top: none; }
    .i-hud-br { bottom: 28px; right: 28px; border-left: none; border-top: none; }

    .i-hero::after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        height: 1px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--gold), transparent);
        opacity: 0.55;
    }

    .i-hero-stage {
        text-align: center;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .i-hero-tag {
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 0.66rem;
        letter-spacing: 3.5px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--gold);
        margin-bottom: var(--s-6);
    }

    .i-hero-pre {
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 0.78rem;
        letter-spacing: 6px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);
        margin: 0 0 var(--s-2);
        text-indent: 6px;
    }

    .i-wordmark {
        font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
        font-variation-settings: 'SOFT' 0;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: clamp(3rem, 7.5vw, 5.4rem);
        letter-spacing: -1.5px;
        color: #fff;
        line-height: 1;
        margin: 0 0 var(--s-6);
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff 30%, rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.7) 100%);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
    }

    .i-hero-tagline {
        font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
        font-style: italic;
        font-weight: 400;
        font-size: 1.35rem;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
        line-height: 1.5;
        letter-spacing: -0.2px;
        max-width: 540px;
        margin: 0 0 var(--s-6);
    }

    .i-hero-meta {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: var(--s-1);
        font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Menlo', monospace;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);
        margin-bottom: var(--s-8);
        padding: 0.5rem 0.95rem;
        background: rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.05);
        border: 1px solid rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.18);
    }

    .i-meta-dot {
        width: 7px;
        height: 7px;
        background: rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.9);
        border-radius: 50%;
        box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.6);
        animation: i-pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes i-pulse {
        0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
        50% { opacity: 0.4; }
    }

    .i-meta-text a {
        color: var(--gold);
        text-decoration: none;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .i-meta-text a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    .i-hero-cta {
        display: flex;
        gap: var(--s-2);
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: center;
    }

    /* ───────────── SHARED ───────────── */
    .i-prose {
        max-width: var(--col-prose);
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 var(--s-3);
    }

    .i-eyebrow {
        display: block;
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        letter-spacing: 2.5px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--gold);
        margin-bottom: var(--s-4);
    }

    .i-eyebrow-gold { color: var(--gold); }

    .i-opening h2,
    .i-cii h2,
    .i-how h2,
    .i-map h2,
    .i-cta h2,
    .i-lede,
    .i-lede-close,
    .i-mod h3 {
        font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
        letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }

    /* ───────────── OPENING ───────────── */
    .i-opening {
        background: var(--cream);
        padding: var(--s-16) 0;
    }

    .i-lede {
        font-weight: 500;
        font-size: 1.75rem;
        line-height: 1.4;
        color: var(--deep-navy);
        margin: 0 0 var(--s-5);
        letter-spacing: -0.4px;
    }

    .i-opening p {
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        line-height: 1.85;
        color: var(--text-medium);
        margin: 0 0 var(--s-4);
    }

    .i-lede-close {
        font-style: italic;
        font-weight: 500;
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        line-height: 1.55;
        color: var(--burgundy);
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border-warm);
        padding-top: var(--s-5);
        margin-top: var(--s-5);
    }

    /* ───────────── CII ───────────── */
    .i-cii {
        background: #0a1628;
        padding: var(--s-16) 0;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .i-cii::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
        height: 1px;
        background: rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.3);
    }

    .i-cii-stage {
        max-width: 820px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 var(--s-3);
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
    }

    .i-cii-head {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: var(--s-8);
    }

    .i-cii-head h2 {
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 2.7rem);
        line-height: 1.15;
        color: #fff;
        margin: 0 0 var(--s-4);
        letter-spacing: -0.8px;
    }

    .i-cii-head p {
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        line-height: 1.85;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .i-formula {
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
        border-left: 2px solid var(--gold);
        padding: var(--s-6) var(--s-6);
        margin: 0 auto var(--s-8);
        max-width: 640px;
    }

    .i-formula-label {
        display: block;
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.65rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 2.5px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--gold);
        margin-bottom: var(--s-4);
    }

    .i-formula-code {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Menlo', monospace;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        line-height: 2;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
        white-space: pre;
        overflow-x: auto;
    }

    .i-fc-v { color: rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.9); }
    .i-fc-n { color: var(--gold); font-weight: 700; }
    .i-fc-op, .i-fc-b { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5); }

    .i-cii-foot {
        max-width: 640px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .i-cii-foot p {
        font-size: 0.98rem;
        line-height: 1.9;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
        margin: 0 0 var(--s-5);
    }

    .i-tag {
        display: inline-block;
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.78rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        padding: 0.2rem 0.55rem;
        margin: 0.15rem;
        white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .i-tag-conf { background: rgba(161, 62, 10, 0.18); color: #d77a40; border: 1px solid rgba(161, 62, 10, 0.3); }
    .i-tag-unr  { background: rgba(139, 21, 56, 0.2);  color: #d8638a; border: 1px solid rgba(139, 21, 56, 0.3); }
    .i-tag-inf  { background: rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.15); color: var(--gold); border: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.3); }
    .i-tag-sec  { background: rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.1); color: rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.9); border: 1px solid rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.25); }

    .i-tier-row {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        align-items: center;
        gap: var(--s-1);
        padding-top: var(--s-5);
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    }

    .i-tier-lbl {
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.65rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        margin-right: var(--s-2);
    }

    .i-tier {
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.72rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 1.5px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        padding: 0.25rem 0.6rem;
    }

    .i-tier-low  { color: #6da17a; background: rgba(109, 161, 122, 0.12); }
    .i-tier-norm { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); }
    .i-tier-elev { color: var(--gold); background: rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.12); }
    .i-tier-high { color: #d77a40; background: rgba(161, 62, 10, 0.18); }
    .i-tier-crit { color: #ff5c7c; background: rgba(255, 92, 124, 0.15); }

    /* ───────────── HOW ───────────── */
    .i-how {
        background: var(--cream);
        padding: var(--s-16) 0;
    }

    .i-how-frame {
        max-width: 820px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 var(--s-3);
    }

    .i-how-head {
        margin-bottom: var(--s-8);
        padding-bottom: var(--s-5);
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(30, 58, 95, 0.1);
    }

    .i-how-head h2 {
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 3.2vw, 2.5rem);
        line-height: 1.18;
        color: var(--deep-navy);
        margin: 0;
    }

    .i-mod {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 64px 1fr;
        gap: var(--s-6);
        padding: var(--s-6) 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(30, 58, 95, 0.08);
    }

    .i-mod:last-of-type { border-bottom: none; }

    .i-mod-num {
        font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
        font-style: italic;
        font-weight: 500;
        font-size: 2rem;
        color: var(--gold);
        line-height: 1;
        padding-top: 0.3rem;
        letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }

    .i-mod h3 {
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 1.4rem;
        color: var(--deep-navy);
        margin: 0 0 var(--s-2);
    }

    .i-mod p {
        font-size: 0.98rem;
        line-height: 1.85;
        color: var(--text-medium);
        margin: 0;
    }

    /* ───────────── MAP & COVERAGE ───────────── */
    .i-map {
        background: var(--stone);
        padding: var(--s-16) 0;
    }

    .i-map h2 {
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: clamp(1.7rem, 2.8vw, 2.2rem);
        line-height: 1.2;
        color: var(--deep-navy);
        margin: 0 0 var(--s-4);
    }

    .i-map p {
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        line-height: 1.85;
        color: var(--text-medium);
        margin: 0;
    }

    .i-cov {
        max-width: 820px;
        margin: var(--s-10) auto 0;
        padding: 0 var(--s-3);
    }

    .i-cov-row {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 220px 1fr;
        gap: var(--s-5);
        padding: var(--s-4) 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(30, 58, 95, 0.1);
        align-items: center;
    }

    .i-cov-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

    .i-cov-cat {
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
